LAIDLEY, Appellant, v. LAIDLEY, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Edward T. Laidley against Etta M. Laidley.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and FOLLETT and PARKER, JJ.

W. S. Bennett, for appellant. W. I. Grow, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
